parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and power brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially when stopping or slowing down.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when coming to a stop
the engine shuts off
the vehicle shudders or bucks when braking
the transmission slips or hesitates
and the vehicle may stall when turning or accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The slipping and stalling of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls when accelerating or decelerating
the vehicle shudders or bucks when shifting gears
and the vehicle may stall when turning or stopping.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine and loss of power can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, especially when stopping or slowing down.
symptoms: The engine stalls when stopping or slowing down
the vehicle loses power
and the vehicle may stall when turning or accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag sensor indicator light shows as "off" with an occupant in the passenger seat
the airbag deploys with a delay
or the airbag fails to deploy altogether.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has led to a delay in the repair of affected vehicles, leaving owners with a safety risk.
symptoms: Owners receive notification of the recall but are unable to schedule a repair due to a lack of available parts
are told to not allow passengers to ride in the front passenger seat
or are not provided with a rental car due to age restrictions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The improper calibration of the passenger airbag sensor can lead to the airbag malfunctioning or not deploying in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The passenger airbag sensor indicator light shows as "off" with an occupant in the passenger seat
even after resetting the sensor or recalibrating the system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusted front sub-frame can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Rust on the front sub-frame
local mechanic declaring the vehicle unsafe to drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the horn can cause distractions while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Horn sounds unintentionally
especially when turning the wheel and accelerating
or when hitting the rim of the steering wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Steering Wheel Remote Radio Volume Control Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering wheel remote radio volume control can cause distractions while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Intermittent to non-operational steering wheel remote radio volume control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the strut mount can cause the vehicle to vibrate and make loud noises, potentially leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Vibrating noise when driving over rough roads
strut mounts may be cracked or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle swaying and drifting can cause loss of control, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle sways side to side at highway speeds
steering pulls extremely
unable to control the steering wheel
vehicle drifts and wanders.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues can cause various malfunctions, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Dash trouble lights flashing constantly
check engine
brake failure
all-wheel drive failure
cruise control failure
temperature light
oil warning light
engine not engaging when gas pedal depressed.
